    "id": 8856886473,
    "title": "Add Script",
    "list_title": "CLIENT CHANGE REQUESTS:",
    "completed": true,
    "due_on": "2025-07-14",
    "created_at": "2025-07-14T20:46:59.465Z",
    "updated_at": "2025-08-04T18:44:45.810Z",
    "completed_on": "2025-07-28T18:30:09.097Z",
    "comments_count": 16,
    "assignees": "Ethan Vandenberg, Keith Bruss, Predrag",
    "app_url": "https://3.basecamp.com/4226914/buckets/42475931/todos/8856886473",
    "description": "<div>\n<bc-attachment sgid=\"BAh7BkkiC19yYWlscwY6BkVUewdJIglkYXRhBjsAVEkiKWdpZDovL2JjMy9QZXJzb24vMzMxMDIwMDA_ZXhwaXJlc19pbgY7AFRJIghwdXIGOwBUSSIPYXR0YWNoYWJsZQY7AFQ=--cf149498ce6489dca0fee35f067c221948f4a465\" content-type=\"application/vnd.basecamp.mention\"><figure>\n  <img data-avatar-for-person-id=\"33102000\" alt=\"Keith Bruss\" title=\"Keith Bruss, CTO at Clixsy\" class=\"avatar\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://bc3-production-assets-cdn.basecamp-static.com/4226914/people/BAhpBLAY+QE=--21688607fb92dc4027e26b291458642ae5c32fcf/avatar\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\">\n  <figcaption>\n    Keith\n  </figcaption>\n</figure></bc-attachment> do you have any concerns for the below? If not I'll add the other devs to the task.<br><br><a href=\"http://onestoputah.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">onestoputah.com</a><br><br>From client:<br><br>Currently, we use ServiceTitan as our CRM and would like to have these requests sent directly to our bookings tab in ServiceTitan. There is a way we can accomplish this using a webform scraper built directly into ServiceTitan, which can be implemented on our site, that will automatically have these form submissions appear within our ServiceTitan account. With that said, prior to making this change, I have included a few notes to be aware of to ensure we can confidently make this change to our site.</div><ul>\n<li>We will want to ensure we are using a supported form provider for the Web Form Attribution to properly connect to our web form. If the form provider is outside of the ones listed, please let us know prior to proceeding. The providers supported are as follows.<ul>\n<li><em>Gravity Forms</em></li>\n<li><em>Contact Form 7</em></li>\n<li><em>Wordpress Forms</em></li>\n<li><em>Elementor Forms</em></li>\n<li><em>Formidable</em></li>\n<li><em>Wix</em></li>\n<li><em>Scorpion</em></li>\n<li><em>Duda</em></li>\n<li><em>Wufoo</em></li>\n<li><em>Ninja Forms</em></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>We will want to make sure we do not have onclick handlers on the webform submission buttons. ServiceTitan relies on the form’s default submit event, so we will want to make sure the submit action isn’t blocked or overridden.</li>\n<li>Lastly, we will want to make sure the form isn't embedded in an iframe. If this is the case, please <strong><em>do not</em></strong> proceed with adding the script.</li>\n</ul><div>After reviewing the notes above, if all is well, please use the code provided below and paste it into the page of our website right before the<strong> &lt;/head&gt;</strong> tag. Once this has been completed, please let me know, and I will test and monitor the form submissions from there!</div><div><br></div><pre>&lt;!-- ServiceTitan DNI --&gt;\n&lt;script&gt;\n    dni = (function(q,w,e,r,t,y,u){q['ServiceTitanDniObject']=t;q[t]=q[t]||function(){\n        (q[t].q=q[t].q||[]).push(arguments)};q[t].l=1*new Date();y=w.createElement(e);\n        u=w.getElementsByTagName(e)[0];y.async=true;y.src=r;u.parentNode.insertBefore(y,u);\n        return q[t];\n    })(window,document,'script','<a href=\"https://static.servicetitan.com/marketing-ads/dni.js\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">https://static.servicetitan.com/marketing-ads/dni.js</a>','dni');\n    dni('init', '1844550432');\n    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() { dni('load'); }, false);\n&lt;/script&gt;\n&lt;!-- ServiceTitan DNI --&gt;</pre>",
    "visible_to_clients": false
  },
